gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 132, Bucks 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Bucks, 132-116. Jordan Clarkson recorded 21 points, four rebounds, and six assists for the Jazz, with Lauri Markkanen adding 21 points and 14 rebounds in the victory. Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied 25 points, 11 assists, and 10 rebounds for the Bucks in the defeat. The Jazz improve to 18-20 in the regular season, while the Bucks fall to 25-12.
